{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Negotiate UK-wide speed limits",
        "additional_details": "We believe a coherent speed limit policy would streamline traffic regulations, promote road safety and facilitate convenient navigation for both residents and visitors. We also consider that consistent speed limits will mitigate confusion and elevate overall road safety measures.\r\n\r\nWe implore the Government to work with the devolved nations on a standardised speed limit policy across the United Kingdom, taking into account the diverse needs and perspectives of all regions and nations within the UK.",
        "background": "We ask the Government to work with the devolved nations to address UK speed limit disparities. We believe standardised speed limit policy is vital for public well-being. Our plea is for a unified approach to speed limits across the UK.",
